  EffectDiscription_ENG: "[Digivolve][Koji Minamoto]: Cost 2 [Digivolve][KendoGarurumon]:
    Cost 1 \n\nYou may digivolve this card from your hand onto one of your yellow
    Tamers as if that card is a level 3 yellow Digimon.\n[When Digivolving] If [KendoGarurumon]
    is in this Digimon's digivolution cards or you have a black or purple Digimon
    or Tamer, this Digimon may digivolve into [AncientGarurumon] in the hand for
